{"tid":2415740,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"瘦到誇張！秀智「側邊開高衩」中空露肚0贅肉　S曲線美炸","createTime":"2021-02-20T13:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T13:22:13.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d044ab4f45c94c78a0bde56c9c227bb9193ee402","tid":2415740,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"南韓「國民初戀」裴秀智（Suzy）從女團miss A成員出道，在團體中就相當亮眼，成為女團門面，不過微肉的身材讓她吃足苦頭，經常吃減肥餐維持鏡頭前的完美女神樣貌，最近她曬出新貼文，短版上衣的中空螞蟻腰全露出來見人，臀圍似乎也小了一圈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/20/3033681-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F20%2F3033681-PH.jpg&h=39ceee80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲裴秀智新廣告照片曝光。（圖／翻攝自skuukzky IG）<br />\n<br />\n秀智最近曬出新貼文，青春洋溢的白底黑點皺摺上衣，搭配超緊身牛仔褲，微微露出小蠻腰，腰間0贅肉讓粉絲全驚呼：「秀智又瘦了！」另外還有白色短板上衣，同樣搭配深色牛仔褲，還能隱約見到大腿縫隙，可見秀智這回是真的瘦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/20/3033683-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F20%2F3033683-PH.jpg&h=61a25741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲裴秀智青春洋溢。（圖／翻攝自skuukzky IG）<br />\n<br />\n另外一組照片更是不得了，秀智身穿黑色連身洋裝，大腿邊開叉到根部，火辣S曲線全都露出，穠纖合度的身材，令人稱羨！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/20/3033682-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F20%2F3033682-PH.jpg&h=a02c8881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲裴秀智中空露出小蠻腰。（圖／翻攝自skuukzky IG）<br />\n<br />\n秀智過去曾說過「自己喝水也會胖」，剛出道甚至還被砲轟是「麵包臉」，公開減肥餐單非常驚人，早上通常只吃雞胸肉和一條地瓜，中午則吃玄米飯搭配沙拉，過了晚上六點就不進食了，除了有減肥餐單外，秀智曾在節目上分享她發明了的居家小運動「企鵝塑身操」，這方法可加強上身訓練，令身材更好看，而且可以防止胸部下垂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/skuukzky/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fskuukzky%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=ca8dce4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/skuukzky/?utm_source=ig_embed</a>"},{"pid":"1270798fe69ed5d22059a3d9b9556ec7fc1d5a61","tid":2415740,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:11:46.000Z","msg":"企鵝塑身操係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n胸部按摩我識"},{"pid":"fcc180e1ae5c2a1269712b4ed8a8d0e4d4513171","tid":2415740,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"無以前咁靚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91657b5c89c15bdc0de05008ecd799602166a2ca","tid":2415740,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fcc180e1ae5c2a1269712b4ed8a8d0e4d4513171","tid":2415740,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"無以前咁靚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:15:31.000Z","msg":"old了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbc51e8c7e62aae2148a720c6621d283dae756f","tid":2415740,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91657b5c89c15bdc0de05008ecd799602166a2ca","tid":2415740,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fcc180e1ae5c2a1269712b4ed8a8d0e4d4513171","tid":2415740,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"無以前咁靚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:15:31.000Z","msg":"old了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:17:47.000Z","msg":"不過都仲係大勝彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2f0701de89aada23ddc70cc9007841a6335bbb","tid":2415740,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fdbc51e8c7e62aae2148a720c6621d283dae756f","tid":2415740,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,